snippet.title: Dinky Kong gameplay
snippet.description:
Dinky Kong, a remake for Pico-8 of the classic arcade Donkey Kong.
Play the game: https://heracleum.itch.io/dinky-kong
Programmed by @Heracleum
Graphics & sound effects by @Trog ( https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?uid=58302 )
Music & sound effects by Trog's son
